flowchart TD

User[User Natural Language Query]

User
    --> APIGW[API Gateway]

APIGW
    --> Orchestrator[Lambda Query Orchestrator]

Orchestrator
    --> DomainSelector[Domain Selector]

DomainSelector
    --> DomainRegistry[Domain Registry]

DomainRegistry
    --> CloudDomain[Cloud Resources Domain]
DomainRegistry
    --> ApiDomain[API Inventory Domain]
DomainRegistry
    --> ChangeDomain[Change Logs Domain]

CloudDomain --> CloudCatalog[Dataset Catalog]
ApiDomain --> ApiCatalog[Dataset Catalog]
ChangeDomain --> ChangeCatalog[Dataset Catalog]

CloudCatalog --> Planner
ApiCatalog --> Planner
ChangeCatalog --> Planner

Planner[LLM Planner NL → QuerySpec]

Planner --> Validator[QuerySpec Validator]

Validator --> Resolver[Dataset Resolver]

Resolver --> SQLBuilder[SQL Builder AST]

SQLBuilder --> CloudDB[(Cloud Resource DB)]
SQLBuilder --> ApiDB[(API Inventory DB)]
SQLBuilder --> ChangeDB[(Change Logs DB)]

CloudDB --> Formatter
ApiDB --> Formatter
ChangeDB --> Formatter

Formatter[Response Formatter]

Formatter --> Response[User Response]
